# PowerShell commands — building-map-explorer

Project folder:

```powershell
cd C:\Users\Robert\Projects\building-map-explorer
```

Local app URL after dev server starts: **http://127.0.0.1:5173/** (or http://localhost:5173/)

---

## Dev server

| Command | When to use |
|---------|-------------|
| `npm run dev` | Normal local dev (keep terminal open) |
| `npm run dev:restart` | Port 5173 stuck / blank page — kills port and restarts |
| `npm run dev:window` | Dev in its own window (survives closing Cursor terminal) |
| `npm run dev:onedrive` | File-watching issues in OneDrive-synced folders |
| `npm run preview` | Preview production build locally |

Restart manually: **Ctrl+C** in dev terminal, then `npm run dev`.

