## Deploy to live site

**App UI / code changes** (buttons, features, `src/`):

```powershell
npm run push-live
```

Custom commit message:

```powershell
npm run push-live -- "fix: describe your change"
```

Push without Manual deploy (push hook only):

```powershell
npm run push-live -- --push-only "fix: describe your change"
```

**Map data + pictures** (portfolio JSON, RTU photos in IndexedDB):

- In the app: **Settings → Sync to Cloudflare & GitHub**
- Needs GitHub token in Settings (`repo` + `workflow` scopes)

**Full update (UI + map data):**

1. `npm run push-live`
2. Settings → **Sync to Cloudflare & GitHub**
3. Hard-refresh live site after ~5–10 min

Live site: https://quadreal-r.github.io/building-map-explorer/  
Actions: https://github.com/quadreal-r/building-map-explorer/actions

