## Git (manual push)

If you prefer git over `push-live`:

```powershell
git pull origin main
git status
git add .
git commit -m "fix: short description"
git push origin main
```

Push rejected (remote ahead — often after Settings sync):

```powershell
git pull origin main
git push origin main
```

**Never commit:** `.env.local`, `deploy-bundle.json`

---

## Sync reports & data

| Command | Purpose |
|---------|---------|
| `npm run report-sync-status` | Excel report in `reports/` (CDN, manifest, sync history) |
| Settings → **Download sync status report** | Same from browser (includes build version, pictures added/removed) |
| `npm run apply-deploy-bundle` | Apply exported `deploy-bundle.json` locally |
| `npm run upload-json-to-r2` | Upload portfolio JSON to Cloudflare R2 |
| `npm run upload-rtu-pictures-r2` | Sync RTU pictures folder to R2 |

