## Cursor / agent shortcuts

| Phrase | Agent should |
|--------|----------------|
| "start server" / "run dev" | `npm run dev` or `npm run dev:restart` |
| "push the code" / "push live" | `npm run push-live` or git pull → test → commit → push |
| "/programmer …" | Implement feature, run tests, ask you to verify before commit |

